00:11:09.602 --> 00:11:12.071
Aku tak boleh rasa seronok kalau kita bersama.

00:11:14.206 --> 00:11:16.175
Saya perlukan sedikit ruang.

00:11:16.742 --> 00:11:17.777
Daripada kami?

